        },
        {
            "+content": "ここは俺に任せて先に行けと言ってから 10年がたったら伝説になっていた。",
            "+@gid": "2998961914",
            "+@type": "Alternative title",
            "+@lang": "JA"
        },
        {
            "+content": "fantasy",
            "+@gid": "971237186",
            "+@type": "Genres"
        },
        {
            "+content": "With no other options, Luck makes the choice to hold the line against the unending demonic hordes alone, to make sure his comrades can escape with their lives. However, through a combination of fortune, skill, and ingenuity, he holds that line for ten straight years, eventually coming out on top single-handedly. Now he has to tackle the dilemma of how to occupy himself in a world where he holds a myriad of roles: that of a legend, that of a veteran, and that of a brand new face.",
            "+@gid": "2400846807",
            "+@type": "Plot Summary"
        },
        {
            "+content": "2026-07-03",
            "+@gid": "2837925299",
            "+@type": "Vintage"
        },
        {
